      • getDeviceIdList

        public void getDeviceIdList(GetDeviceIdListEvent event)
        Description copied from interface: DeviceServicesListener
        Indicates that a list of devices is available from a GetDeviceIdList request. The GetDeviceIdListEvent contains a portion of the list of devices that was retrieved from a GetDeviceIdList request. Multiple GetDeviceIdListEvents may be received on a single request depending on how many devices are on the server for the session. See the GetDeviceIdListEvent request for more information.
        Specified by:
        getDeviceIdList in interface DeviceServicesListener
        Parameters:
        event - list of devices

      • getMonitorList

        public void getMonitorList(GetMonitorListEvent event)
        Description copied from interface: DeviceServicesListener
        Indicates that a list of DeviceIDs is available from a GetMonitorList request. The GetMonitorListEvent contains a portion of the list of devices and their associated monitors that was retrieved from a GetMonitorList request. Multiple GetMonitorListEvents may be received on a single request depending on how many devices and monitors are on the server for the session. See the GetMonitorListEvent request for more information.
        Specified by:
        getMonitorList in interface DeviceServicesListener
        Parameters:
        event - list of devices and their associated monitors.

The TransferMonitorObjectsEvent contains a portion of the list of devices that was retrieved from a TransferMonitorObjects request. Multiple TransferMonitorObjectsEvents may be received on a single request depending on how many devices are on the server for the session. See the TransferMonitorObjectsEvent request for more information.
        Specified by:
